{"tid":2218344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"再創記錄 美軍EP-3E電偵機抵廣東偵察，離中國最近僅47.81海哩","createTime":"2020-09-26T06:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T13:07:36.000Z","uid":44209,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"73f49d38d51914b26b0d9f07cc768c228ae138df","tid":2218344,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"美軍今晨派出1架EP-3E電偵機和一架P8A巡邏機抵廣東偵察，離中國最近僅47.81海哩。<br />\n<br />\nUSN EP-3E and P-8A are patrolling over the #SouthChinaSea. Of which, the EP-3E is as nearest as 47.81NM of Guang Dong coast of China. Sep,26.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vzhq3dp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvzhq3dp.jpg&h=f851b94f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imMO0Z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimMO0Z6.jpg&h=19bb368c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/scs_pi/status/1309675559601889280?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fscs_pi%2Fstatus%2F1309675559601889280%3Fs%3D21&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=70fd5085\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fscs_pi%2Fstatus%2F1309675559601889280%3Fs%3D21&h=f2a9b7b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/scs_pi/status/1309675559601889280?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"6d640594199577c757c8e620f4f8a7c669ec6e6b","tid":2218344,"uid":26045,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"你唔認中線咁我咪跟你唔認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a0d979f970ba6d49d9b324a2c7d83c2b15265a","tid":2218344,"uid":44209,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"6d640594199577c757c8e620f4f8a7c669ec6e6b","tid":2218344,"uid":26045,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"你唔認中線咁我咪跟你唔認囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAWvuUr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAWvuUr.gif&h=2dc3af6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee6e6becf84d28700b0cff332058ee08ecc58fac","tid":2218344,"uid":44209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"〔記者羅添斌／台北報導〕中國接連多日出動軍機侵擾台灣西南空域，甚至派出軍機刻意越過中線挑釁，美軍今天則是派出軍機對中國進行抵近偵察，最近的距離僅有47.81浬（約合88.5公里），再次刷新美國軍機對中國抵近偵察距離最近的記錄。<br />\n<br />\n美軍今年以來多次派出軍機到東海丶南海偵察，並且對中國大陸進行抵近偵察，掌握共軍的活動動態，但大多保持距離中國大陸沿海50浬（約合92.6公里）以上，但今天的抵近偵察行動則是切進50浬之內的距離，明顯是中國解放軍施壓，測試共軍的壓力底線。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/3303770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3303770&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=06169ec6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3303770&h=2a33cc9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/3303770</a>"},{"pid":"00ca8667d64ef0a140181f3a89481beab6119010","tid":2218344,"uid":198181,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQRzb9Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQRzb9Q.jpg&h=6a73e0bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76fe9d4d7c75fd794d81dc6ee2099bf68b2454d2","tid":2218344,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9a9ac0cd1b